    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Adepta Sororitas</h2><p>The Adepta Sororitas — the Sisters of Battle — are the militant arm of the Ecclesiarchy, warrior-women whose faith in the God-Emperor is matched only by their ferocity in battle. Raised in the Schola Progenium and forged in the fires of devotion, they are trained in both the arts of war and the social graces of the Imperial Creed. Those who serve an Inquisitor of the Ordo Hereticus bring unshakeable conviction, martial skill, and an intimate knowledge of the Ecclesiarchy's inner workings.</p><h3>Background Aptitudes</h3><p>Offence, Social</p><h3>Starting Skills</h3><p>Athletics, Charm or Intimidate, Common Lore (Adepta Sororitas), Linguistics (High Gothic), Medicae or Parry</p><h3>Starting Talent</h3><p>Weapon Training (Chain, Flame, or Las)</p><h3>Background Bonus</h3><p><strong>Incorruptible Devotion:</strong> Whenever an Adepta Sororitas character spends a Fate Point to resist mind control or Corruption, she gains a +20 bonus to the Test instead of the normal reroll.</p>"
    },
